title: Match of the Day 2014-02-12 720p 50fps HDTV x264-wAm.mkv
description:
SPORT: Match of the Day
On: BBC 1 HD    
Date: Wednesday 12th February 2014

Gary Lineker presents highlights from Premier League.


Notes:
Captured and encoded at 50fps to give much smoother playback. 

I strongly advise you to use MPC-HC with MadVR filter. In MadVR settings go to Rendering-Smooth Motion and enable for 'only if the would be no motion judder'.
